{"tid":1398683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"范徐麗泰：外國有人想「一國兩制」失敗","createTime":"2019-08-03T01:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T05:22:45.000Z","uid":20933,"like":6,"dislike":127,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"d0e72b8bf3a05ec819f0b93e2f5b292220b896b1","tid":1398683,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T01:59:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/FORUM-RITA-190803-09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FFORUM-RITA-190803-09.jpg&h=8903e921&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】全國人大前常委范徐麗泰在本台節目大鳴大放中表示，待現時修訂逃犯條例的爭議平息後，可考慮成立律師會建議的非法定調查委員會。她又質疑，外國有人想一國兩制失敗，搗亂香港，迫使駐港解放軍出動，讓西方國家有機會批評中國，阻礙國家發展。<br />\n<br />\n反對修訂逃犯條例的示威遊行持續近兩個月，爆發多場警民衝突。<br />\n<br />\n全國人大前常委范徐麗泰質疑，連場示威有外國勢力參與，目的是想一國兩制失敗，令香港出現混亂，阻礙中國發展。<br />\n<br />\n范徐麗泰又認為，現時成立獨立調查委員會，調查範圍只會引起更多爭拗，反而可考慮待局勢緩和後，參考律師會建議成立非法定調查委員會，讓證人匿名作供，相信更有效找出這次風波的成因，避免再犯。<br />\n<br />\n范徐麗泰又表示，有很多反共的教師將對中國的反感灌輸給學生，應該反思教育制度是否出現問題，致令現時出現這批年青人。"},{"pid":"182b323f61ed5d731a043e6da1b2c4f762d38cf6","tid":1398683,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T01:59:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=357773\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D357773&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDeu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=a1d76d42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D357773&h=49f79bb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=357773</a>"},{"pid":"26adb91b4ec50c33afe9bea2e7b1071f9f43e20b","tid":1398683,"uid":18604,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:00:27.000Z","msg":"繼續9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返學從來無聽過老師上堂攻擊支那"},{"pid":"78c6817aa6e3f199e0d6a3396797da1d5baf3002","tid":1398683